title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: It's another Friday Football Feast with PA and Charch, with a week to go for the NFL Draft. PA's conversation with Tom Pelissero. Chad Greenway makes his weekly appearance and to talk the new class coming into the NFL this year, and Professional Sports Card Collector, Eric Meyers calls in.
